commentTextItems.html: flatter outside off and he slogs that over point and with it a series win

commentPostTextItems.html: Zimbabwe has won the series with the hosts left to try and salvage a whitewash. It was a tight game that swung both ways but Ongondo's crazy over was all that Zimbabwe needed
Thank you for staying with us and do please join us again tomorrow for the fourth ODI

stories.title: Utseya leads Zimbabwe to series win
stories.subTitle: Kenya v ZImbabwe, 3rd ODI, Nairobi
stories.summary: Prosper Utseya played an outstanding captain's innings to lead Zimbabwe to a series-clinching four-wicket win in the third ODI in Nairobi after the home side had looked on course to keep the contest alive
